### Supermarket Stock Prediction API - HTTP Test File
### 
### This file can be used with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools
### to test the prediction service endpoints.
###
### Prerequisites:
### 1. Set MODEL_BACKEND=onnx environment variable
### 2. Start the server: python -m server.main
### 3. Server runs on http://127.0.0.1:8000

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================
### Health Check Endpoint
### ============================================

### Health Check - Verify server is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ============================================
### Prediction Endpoints (ONNX Model)
### ============================================

### Basic Prediction - 7 day forecast
### Tests ONNX model with minimal required fields
### Horizon is calculated from start_date to end_date (inclusive)
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "product_id": "PROD001",
  "store_id": "STORE001",
  "start_date": "2024-12-17",
  "end_date": "2024-12-23"
}

### ============================================

### Extended Prediction - 14 day forecast
### Tests ONNX model with longer horizon
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "product_id": "PROD123",
  "store_id": "STORE456",
  "start_date": "2024-12-17",
  "end_date": "2024-12-30"
}

