### Tests ONNX model with full month horizon
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "product_id": "PROD_MONTHLY",
  "store_id": "STORE_MONTHLY",
  "start_date": "2024-12-17",
